{"tid":1156752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亮劍 宣佈國家緊急狀態 美國總統特朗普簽禁令封殺華為","createTime":"2019-05-15T21:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T05:27:16.000Z","uid":125193,"like":110,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6d87cedf686b29d479407931f5dc5626502dc1e6","tid":1156752,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T21:31:19.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰火怒燒之際，美國總統特朗普周三簽署行政命令，宣佈國家緊急狀態，禁止美國企業使用對美國國家安全構成風險的企業的電訊設備，劍指全球第一電訊設備製造商、中國華為。<br />\n<br />\n行政命令援引美國《國際緊急狀態經濟權力法》（International Emergency Economic Powers Act），賦予美國總統在國家面臨緊急狀態威脅時，進行商業管制權力。命令指示，美國商務部與其他政府機構合作，制訂執行計劃。<br />\n<br />\n命令沒有點名企業或國家，但顯然為禁止美企和華為做生意。<br />\n<br />\n此行政命令是特朗普自去年8月簽署《2019年度國防授權法》，禁止美國政府使用華為及中興兩間中國公司的設備以來，另一封殺華為的行動。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"19a46e53e3d0c065ede08669611bf42f46dab645","tid":1156752,"uid":201604,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T21:31:51.000Z","msg":"是但啦 中國又贏"},{"pid":"98c8acc6736785e6f3e60166c65e418f8238c225","tid":1156752,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T21:34:21.000Z","msg":"【華為危機】宣佈國家緊急狀態 特朗普簽禁令封殺華為<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190516&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59605767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190516%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59605767&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2PMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=d2936d9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190516%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59605767&h=51435804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190516&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59605767</a>"},{"pid":"51c2c1d99ecdb255abc48125ee63a01827e84abd","tid":1156752,"uid":164387,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T21:36:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fdb4f11f0467b6da34579efe81dff7990cfd62f","tid":1156752,"uid":238370,"like":4,"dislike":24,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"51c2c1d99ecd